    "start_blocks": "// Variables for car and object positions\r\nvar carX = 160;\r\nvar carY = 240;\r\nvar objectX = randomNumber(40, 280);\r\nvar objectY = randomNumber(40, 410);\r\nvar score = 0;\r\nvar scenarioActive = false;\r\nvar currentScenario = \"\"; // Tracks the active scenario\r\nvar slowPerformanceActive = false; // Tracks if slow performance is active\r\nvar errorStep = 0; // Tracks steps in resolving error messages\r\nvar permissionStep = 0; // Tracks steps in resolving permission errors;\r\n\r\n// Initialize game\r\ninitializeGame();\r\nfunction initializeGame() {\r\n  setScreen(\"gameScreen\"); // Ensure game starts on the game screen\r\n  setText(\"scoreLabel\", \"Score: \" + score);\r\n  setPosition(\"car\", carX, carY, 50, 50); // Car sprite\r\n  setPosition(\"object\", objectX, objectY, 30, 30); // Collectible object\r\n  timedLoop(1000, function() {\r\n    if (!scenarioActive) {\r\n      checkCollision();\r\n    }\r\n  });\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n// Move car using arrow keys\r\nonEvent(\"gameScreen\", \"keydown\", function(event) {\r\n  moveCar(event);\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction moveCar(event) {\r\n  if (!scenarioActive) {\r\n    var movementSpeed = slowPerformanceActive ? 2 : 10; // Slow performance effect reduces movement speed\r\n\r\n    if (event.key === \"Left\") {\r\n      carX = Math.max(0, carX - movementSpeed);\r\n    }\r\n    if (event.key === \"Right\") {\r\n      carX = Math.min(320, carX + movementSpeed);\r\n    }\r\n    if (event.key === \"Up\") {\r\n      carY = Math.max(0, carY - movementSpeed);\r\n    }\r\n    if (event.key === \"Down\") {\r\n      carY = Math.min(480, carY + movementSpeed);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    setPosition(\"car\", carX, carY);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n// Check for collision\r\nfunction checkCollision() {\r\n  if (Math.abs(carX - objectX) < 30 && Math.abs(carY - objectY) < 30) {\r\n    score += 10;\r\n    setText(\"scoreLabel\", \"Score: \" + score);\r\n    objectX = randomNumber(40, 280);\r\n    objectY = randomNumber(40, 410);\r\n    setPosition(\"object\", objectX, objectY);\r\n\r\n    // Randomly trigger a troubleshooting scenario\r\n    if (randomNumber(1, 4) == 1) {\r\n      triggerScenario();\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// Trigger a troubleshooting scenario and switch to troubleshooting screen\r\nfunction triggerScenario() {\r\n  scenarioActive = true; // Stop gameplay\r\n  setScreen(\"troubleshootingScreen\");\r\n\r\n  var scenario = randomNumber(1, 4); // Random scenario type\r\n  if (scenario == 1) {\r\n    currentScenario = \"error\";\r\n    errorScenario();\r\n  }\r\n  if (scenario == 2) {\r\n    currentScenario = \"permission\";\r\n    permissionScenario();\r\n  }\r\n  if (scenario == 3) {\r\n    currentScenario = \"crash\";\r\n    crashScenario();\r\n  }\r\n  if (scenario == 4) {\r\n    currentScenario = \"slow\";\r\n    slowPerformanceScenario();\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// Scenario: Error Messages\r\nfunction errorScenario() {\r\n  setText(\"errorLabel\", \"Fatal Exception: Memory Allocation Error\");\r\n  setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Select an action to attempt a resolution.\");\r\n  errorStep = 0;\r\n  showButtons([\"Free Up Memory\", \"Check Logs\", \"Restart Driver\", \"Ignore\", \"Install Patch\", \"Increase RAM\"]);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction resolveError(action) {\r\n  if (action === \"Free Up Memory\" && errorStep === 0) {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"No improvement. Additional action required.\");\r\n    errorStep++;\r\n    showButtons([\"Restart Driver\", \"Check for Updates\", \"Clear Cache\", \"Ignore\", \"Disable Auto-save\", \"Change Power Plan\"]);\r\n  } else if (action === \"Restart Driver\" && errorStep === 1) {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Error Resolved!\");\r\n    resumeGameplay();\r\n  } else {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Action failed. Try another.\");\r\n    setTimeout(function() {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"\");\r\n    },1000);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// Scenario: Permission Errors\r\nfunction permissionScenario() {\r\n  setText(\"errorLabel\", \"Access Blocked: Insufficient Permissions\");\r\n  setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Choose an action.\");\r\n  permissionStep = 0;\r\n  showButtons([\"Run as Admin\", \"Request Permission\", \"Check Network\", \"Ignore\", \"Reset Permissions\", \"Try Guest Account\"]);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction resolvePermission(action) {\r\n  if (action === \"Request Permission\" && permissionStep === 0) {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Access Denied. Try another action.\");\r\n    permissionStep++;\r\n    showButtons([\"Run as Admin\", \"Disable Security\", \"Reinstall Program\", \"Ignore\", \"Edit Group Policy\", \"Retry with Different User\"]);\r\n  } else if (action === \"Run as Admin\" && permissionStep === 1) {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Access Granted!\");\r\n    resumeGameplay();\r\n  } else {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Action failed. Try another.\");\r\n    setTimeout(function() {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"\");\r\n    },1000);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// Scenario: Program Crashes\r\nfunction crashScenario() {\r\n  setText(\"errorLabel\", \"Application Crashed: Unknown Error\");\r\n  setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"What would you like to try?\");\r\n  showButtons([\"Check Logs\", \"Force Quit\", \"Wait for Response\", \"Restart Program\", \"Uninstall and Reinstall\", \"Adjust Virtual Memory\"]);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction resolveCrash(action) {\r\n  if (action === \"Force Quit\") {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Program force quit. Restart required.\");\r\n    resumeGameplay();\r\n  } else if (action === \"Restart Program\") {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Program restarted successfully!\");\r\n    resumeGameplay();\r\n  } else {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Action failed. Try another.\");\r\n    setTimeout(function() {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"\");\r\n    },1000);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// Scenario: Slow Performance\r\nfunction slowPerformanceScenario() {\r\n  slowPerformanceActive = true;\r\n  setText(\"errorLabel\", \"Application Running Slowly\");\r\n  setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Choose an action to optimize performance.\");\r\n  showButtons([\"Clear Cache\", \"Upgrade Memory\", \"End Background Tasks\", \"Ignore\", \"Lower Graphics Settings\", \"Enable Performance Mode\"]);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction resolveSlowPerformance(action) {\r\n  if (action === \"Clear Cache\") {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Cache cleared. Problem persists.\");\r\n    showButtons([\"Upgrade Memory\", \"Disable Animations\", \"End Background Tasks\", \"Ignore\", \"Adjust Power Settings\", \"Check Task Manager\"]);\r\n  } else if (action === \"Upgrade Memory\") {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Performance Restored!\");\r\n    slowPerformanceActive = false;\r\n    resumeGameplay();\r\n  } else {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"Action failed. Try another.\");\r\n    setTimeout(function() {\r\n    setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"\");\r\n    },1000);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// Universal resolver for all scenarios\r\nfunction resolveScenario(action) {\r\n  if (currentScenario === \"error\") resolveError(action);\r\n  if (currentScenario === \"permission\") resolvePermission(action);\r\n  if (currentScenario === \"crash\") resolveCrash(action);\r\n  if (currentScenario === \"slow\") resolveSlowPerformance(action);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// Event listeners for buttons\r\nonEvent(\"button1\", \"click\", function() {\r\n  resolveScenario(getText(\"button1\"));\r\n});\r\nonEvent(\"button2\", \"click\", function() {\r\n  resolveScenario(getText(\"button2\"));\r\n});\r\nonEvent(\"button3\", \"click\", function() {\r\n  resolveScenario(getText(\"button3\"));\r\n});\r\nonEvent(\"button4\", \"click\", function() {\r\n  resolveScenario(getText(\"button4\"));\r\n});\r\nonEvent(\"button5\", \"click\", function() {\r\n  resolveScenario(getText(\"button5\"));\r\n});\r\nonEvent(\"button6\", \"click\", function() {\r\n  resolveScenario(getText(\"button6\"));\r\n});\r\n\r\n// Resume gameplay after resolving scenarios\r\nfunction resumeGameplay() {\r\n  scenarioActive = false; // Resume gameplay\r\n  setText(\"errorLabel\", \"\");\r\n  setText(\"feedbackLabel\", \"\");\r\n  hideAllButtons();\r\n  setScreen(\"gameScreen\");\r\n  setText(\"messageLabel\", \"Nice Troubleshooting!\");\r\n  setTimeout(function() {\r\n    setText(\"messageLabel\", \"\");\r\n    },1000);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction showButtons(options) {\r\n  hideAllButtons();\r\n  \r\n  // Shuffle the options array to randomize button placement\r\n  options = shuffleArray(options);\r\n\r\n  for (var i = 0; i < options.length; i++) {\r\n    showElement(\"button\" + (i + 1));\r\n    setText(\"button\" + (i + 1), options[i]);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// Fisher-Yates shuffle algorithm to randomize array order\r\nfunction shuffleArray(array) {\r\n  var currentIndex = array.length, temporaryValue, randomIndex;\r\n\r\n  while (currentIndex !== 0) {\r\n    randomIndex = Math.floor(Math.random() * currentIndex);\r\n    currentIndex--;\r\n\r\n    // Swap current element with a random one\r\n    temporaryValue = array[currentIndex];\r\n    array[currentIndex] = array[randomIndex];\r\n    array[randomIndex] = temporaryValue;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  return array;\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction hideAllButtons() {\r\n  for (var i = 1; i <= 6; i++) {\r\n    hideElement(\"button\" + i);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n",
    "start_html": "<div id=\"designModeViz\" class=\"appModern clip-content\" data-radium=\"true\" style=\"width: 320px; height: 450px; display: block;\"><div class=\"screen\" tabindex=\"1\" data-theme=\"default\" id=\"gameScreen\" style=\"display: block; height: 450px; width: 320px; left: 0px; top: 0px; position: absolute; z-index: 0; background-color: rgb(232, 243, 207);\"><img data-canonical-image-url=\"icon://fa-car\" data-image-type=\"icon\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"car\" style=\"height: 60px; width: 45px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 115px; top: 80px; margin: 0px;\"><label style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 320px; border-style: solid; text-rendering: optimizespeed; color: rgb(77, 87, 95); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 15px; width: 245px; height: 45px; position: absolute; left: 40px; top: 400px;\" id=\"messageLabel\">Use the arrow keys to move the car around!</label><label style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 320px; border-style: solid; text-rendering: optimizespeed; color: rgb(77, 87, 95); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding: 2px 15px; width: 160px; height: 30px; position: absolute; left: 20px; top: 15px;\" id=\"scoreLabel\"></label><img data-canonical-image-url=\"icon://fa-star-o\" data-image-type=\"icon\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"object\" style=\"height: 60px; width: 45px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 130px; top: 165px; margin: 0px;\"></div><div class=\"screen\" tabindex=\"1\" data-theme=\"default\" id=\"troubleshootingScreen\" style=\"display: none; height: 450px; width: 320px; left: 0px; top: 0px; position: absolute; z-index: 0; background-color: rgb(239, 219, 219);\"><button id=\"button1\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 55px; width: 145px; background-color: rgb(255, 164, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 10px; top: 90px;\" class=\"design-mode-hidden\">Button</button><button id=\"button2\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 55px; width: 145px; background-color: rgb(255, 164, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 170px; top: 90px;\" class=\"design-mode-hidden\">Button</button><button id=\"button5\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 55px; width: 145px; background-color: rgb(255, 164, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 170px; top: 165px;\" class=\"design-mode-hidden\">Button</button><button id=\"button6\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 55px; width: 145px; background-color: rgb(255, 164, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 170px; top: 240px;\" class=\"design-mode-hidden\">Button</button><button id=\"button4\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 55px; width: 145px; background-color: rgb(255, 164, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 10px; top: 240px;\" class=\"design-mode-hidden\">Button</button><button id=\"button3\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 55px; width: 145px; background-color: rgb(255, 164, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 10px; top: 165px;\" class=\"design-mode-hidden\">Button</button><label style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 320px; border-style: solid; text-rendering: optimizespeed; color: rgb(77, 87, 95); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding: 2px 15px; width: 290px; height: 70px; position: absolute; left: 15px; top: 10px; text-align: center;\" id=\"errorLabel\"></label><label style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 320px; border-style: solid; text-rendering: optimizespeed; color: rgb(77, 87, 95); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding: 2px 15px; width: 290px; height: 70px; position: absolute; left: 20px; top: 330px; text-align: center;\" id=\"feedbackLabel\"></label></div></div>",
    "long_instructions": "# Welcome to the Troubleshooting Simulation!\r\n\r\n### **Step 1: Explore the Simulation**\r\n\r\n\r\n**Do This:** Use the **arrow keys** to move the car on the screen and interact with the game environment. Here's what to expect:\r\n\r\n- **Goal**: Collect stars on the screen to earn points.\r\n- **Challenges**: Occasionally, your system will encounter problems (e.g., slow performance, crashes, or errors).\r\n- When an issue arises, the system will:\r\n  - Display a message describing the problem.\r\n  - Provide a set of potential actions for you to try.\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### **Step 2: Resolve System Issues**\r\n\r\n\r\nWhen a problem appears:\r\n1. **Read the Message**: Carefully review the problem that has occurred (e.g., \"Application Crashed: Unknown Error\").\r\n2. **Try Different Actions**:\r\n   - Use the buttons on the screen to test possible solutions.\r\n   - Some actions will help, while others might make things worse or have no effect. Think critically about what might work!\r\n3. **Observe Feedback**:\r\n   - Pay attention to how the system responds to your actions. If one solution doesn’t work, try another!\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### **Tips for Success**\r\n\r\n\r\n- **Experiment**: Not every action will work, and that's okay! The goal is to figure out what steps are most effective for each type of problem.\r\n- **Communicate**: If you're working with a partner, talk through your reasoning before trying each action.\r\n- **Keep Track**: Pay attention to what actions resolve problems and what actions don’t. This will help you refine your troubleshooting approach.\r\n\r\n",
    "name_suffix": "_v2-2025",
    "preload_asset_list": null
